<section id="social-proof" class="py-16 bg-secondary-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-4 text-primary-900 font-bold"
        >
          Post-Raise Mistakes Founders Regret
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Avoid the financial pitfalls most teams don't see coming — until it's a problem.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Block 1 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex flex-col h-full"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-accent-500 mr-3"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Finance Lags Behind the Raise</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4 flex-grow">
            Most founders keep using spreadsheets and intuition after raising. New capital brings new expectations, finance needs to catch up fast.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 mt-auto">
            → Avoid this: Set up real systems before your board asks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 2 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex flex-col h-full"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-accent-500 mr-3"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">No Metrics, No Decisions</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4 flex-grow">
            Manual reports, no cash visibility, and missing dashboards are the norm post-raise. It kills decision-making and trust with investors.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 mt-auto">
            → Avoid this: Automate reporting and build clarity early.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 3 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex flex-col h-full"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-accent-500 mr-3"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Ops Scales, Finance Doesn't</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-4 flex-grow">
            Startups often scale teams, but skip finance hires. Without financial oversight, burn creeps, payroll breaks, and the chaos snowballs.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 mt-auto">
            → Avoid this: Bring in C-level financial support before it breaks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/mhachicha-crownacquisitiongroup"
          class="inline-block bg-primary-700 hover:bg-primary-600 text-white font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Get Financial Clarity
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
